short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Analyzes and highlights videos 30% above the median view count on a YouTube channel page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Spy on your competition to see which videos perform the best against the channels' median value. Analyze the data for more views and subscribers!

IMPORTANT!

The plugin ONLY works with the following URL structure:

https://www.youtube.com/@Channel/videos

If the plugin is not responding, just refresh the url you're analysing.
